---
---
<section class="about-author">
  <div class="author-image-wrapper">
    <img src="/images/posts/default.jpg" alt="Author" class="author-image" loading="lazy" />
  </div>
  <div class="author-info">
    <h2 class="author-heading">About the Author</h2>
    <p class="author-bio">
      Welcome to my digital space. I'm a writer, thinker, and lifelong learner exploring the intersection of philosophy, science, and the human experience.
      <br/><br/>
      Through these essays, I hope to spark curiosity and inspire others to wander through the landscape of ideas with an open mind.
    </p>
    <div class="author-socials">
      <a href="#" aria-label="Twitter">
        <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M22 4s-.7 2.1-2 3.4c1.6 10-9.4 17.3-18 11.6 2.2.1 4.4-.6 6-2C3 15.5.5 9.6 3 5c2.2 2.6 5.6 4.1 9 4-.9-4.2 4-6.6 7-3.8 1.1 0 3-1.2 3-1.2z"/></svg>
      </a>
      <a href="#" aria-label="LinkedIn">
        <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M16 8a6 6 0 0 1 6 6v7h-4v-7a2 2 0 0 0-2-2 2 2 0 0 0-2 2v7h-4v-7a6 6 0 0 1 6-6z"/><rect width="4" height="12" x="2" y="9"/><circle cx="4" cy="4" r="2"/></svg>
      </a>
      <a href="#" aria-label="Instagram">
        <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><rect width="20" height="20" x="2" y="2" rx="5" ry="5"/><path d="M16 11.37A4 4 0 1 1 12.63 8 4 4 0 0 1 16 11.37z"/><line x1="17.5" x2="17.51" y1="6.5" y2="6.5"/></svg>
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .about-author {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 60px;
    align-items: center;
    margin: 100px 0;
  }
  .author-image-wrapper {
    border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
    overflow: hidden;
    height: 400px;
  }
  .author-image {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    object-fit: cover;
  }
  .author-heading {
    font-family: var(--font-heading);
    font-size: 2.2rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    margin-bottom: 24px;
    color: var(--text-primary);
  }
  .author-bio {
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    line-height: 1.7;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    margin-bottom: 32px;
  }
  .author-socials {
    display: flex;
    gap: 16px;
  }
  .author-socials a {
    color: var(--text-primary);
    transition: color 0.2s ease;
    width: 20px;
    height: 20px;
  }
  .author-socials a:hover {
    color: var(--text-muted);
  }
  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .about-author {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 40px;
    }
    .author-image-wrapper {
      height: 300px;
    }
  }
</style>
